{"tid":386762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支聯會海祭劉曉波","createTime":"2017-09-04T06:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T06:38:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"69f93637fbeb87076da60f963a74df2380e2419a","tid":386762,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:38:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20142230&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170904\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20142230%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170904&d=ZHrH1%2FwvHXf6jfny9QUxDzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=827b02be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20142230%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170904&h=7e05cc9c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20142230&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170904</a><br />\n<br />\n支聯會海祭劉曉波<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n        <img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170904/large/04la8p04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170904%2Flarge%2F04la8p04.jpg&h=47d75fe5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支聯會昨到西貢「曉波徑」附近石灘舉行海祭，悼念因肝癌去世的諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波，並要求中共立即釋放劉霞。參與人士默哀後，把寫上「自由、抗爭、希望」的空凳送出海，並蒐集碎石砌出「Free Liu Xia」字樣（圖）。支聯會秘書李卓人表示，劉曉波「被海葬」是連入土為安的權利都被剝奪；劉霞失去自由，亦不能為亡夫立碑，要服抗鬱藥度日。<br />\n張志華攝"}]}